history.command: DECLARE person_nodes AS LIST WITH_DESCRIPTION "All PERSON nodes from the graph"

extraction.description: All PERSON nodes from the graph

history.command: FIND nodes with entity_type=PERSON AS person_nodes
PROCESS person_nodes with instruction: extract first name from description and store as first_name
PROCESS person_nodes with instruction: create boolean field starts_with_vowel, true if first_name starts with A, E, I, O, or U (case-insensitive), else false
COUNT person_nodes where starts_with_vowel = true AS vowel_count
COUNT person_nodes where starts_with_vowel = false AS non_vowel_count
COUNT person_nodes field first_name where starts_with_vowel = true AS vowel_count;
COUNT person_nodes field first_name where starts_with_vowel = false AS non_vowel_count;
